Name: Average time for Completed + Cancelled across all process variants where it occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Total time from Accepted + In Progress to Completed + Cancelled
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time it takes Completed + Cancelled to be done after Accepted + Wait - User
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Time from Accepted + Wait - Vendor to Completed + Cancelled
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Elapsed time between Accepted + Assigned and Completed + Cancelled
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time for Completed + Cancelled in variants that also contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Total time for Completed + Cancelled when preceded by Accepted + Wait - Implementation
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Minimum time it takes Completed + Cancelled after the execution of Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Time of Completed + Cancelled in cases where Completed + In Call appears earlier in the same trace
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time until Completed + Cancelled is performed in variants starting with Queued + Awaiting Assignment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Total resolution time of Completed + Cancelled when the case includes at least one Completed + In Call activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Time from Completed + In Call to Completed + Cancelled within the same case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time for Completed + Cancelled grouped by country
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Minimum time for Completed + Cancelled in traces that transition through Accepted + Wait - Customer
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Elapsed time between Unmatched + Unmatched and Completed + Cancelled
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Total time it takes Completed + Cancelled after the last occurrence of Completed + In Call in the trace
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Time until Completed + Cancelled is performed following a direct path from Accepted + In Progress without intermediate queuing
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Minimum time from Completed + Resolved to Completed + Cancelled
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average cycle time of Completed + Cancelled in variants that do not contain any wait states (e.g., no Accepted + Wait - *)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'
